<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
<meta name="robots" content="index, follow">
<title>Legal & Privacy — Ziezi Labs</title>
<style>
  :root { color-scheme: light dark; }
  * { box-sizing: border-box; }
  body {
    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    background: #ffffff;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 1.25rem;
  }
  main { max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto; }
  h1 { font-size: 1.6rem; line-height: 1.25; margin: 0 0 0.25rem; }
  h2 { font-size: 1.2rem; margin: 2rem 0 0.5rem; border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e2e2; padding-bottom: 0.3rem; }
  p, li { font-size: 1rem; }
  a { color: #0a58ca; word-break: break-word; }
  code { background: #f1f1f1; padding: 0.1rem 0.35rem; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 0.92em; }
  .tagline { color: #555; font-size: 1.05rem; margin: 0.25rem 0 1.5rem; }
  .apps { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0.5rem 0; }
  .apps > li {
    border: 1px solid #e2e2e2;
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 0.9rem 1rem;
    margin: 0.75rem 0;
  }
  .apps h3 { margin: 0 0 0.3rem; font-size: 1.1rem; }
  .apps .pkg { color: #777; font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: normal; }
  .apps .docs { margin: 0.4rem 0 0; padding: 0; list-style: none; }
  .apps .docs li { display: inline-block; margin: 0.15rem 0.75rem 0.15rem 0; font-size: 0.97rem; }
  footer { margin-top: 2.5rem; padding-top: 1rem; border-top: 1px solid #e2e2e2; color: #555; font-size: 0.9rem; }
  @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
    body { color: #e6e6e6; background: #121212; }
    h1 { color: #f2f2f2; }
    h2 { border-bottom-color: #333; }
    a { color: #6ea8fe; }
    code { background: #2a2a2a; }
    .tagline, .apps .pkg, footer { color: #aaa; }
    .apps > li { border-color: #333; }
    footer { border-top-color: #333; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<main>

  <h1>Ziezi Labs — Legal &amp; Privacy</h1>
  <p class="tagline">
    This site hosts the privacy policies and related legal documents for apps published by
    <strong>Ziezi Labs</strong>.
  </p>

  <h2>Apps</h2>
  <ul class="apps">
    <li>
      <h3>Toolbelt <span class="pkg">(<code>dev.toolbelt.app</code>)</span></h3>
      <p>Calculator and reference tools for tradespeople.</p>
      <ul class="docs">
        <li><a href="toolbelt/privacy.html">Privacy Policy &rarr;</a></li>
        <li><a href="toolbelt/terms.html">Terms of Service &rarr;</a></li>
      </ul>
    </li>
  </ul>
  <p style="color:#777;font-size:0.92rem;">More apps and documents will be listed here as they are published.</p>

  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <p>
    For questions about any document on this site, contact
    <a href="mailto:zzhelev+ziezilabs@gmail.com">zzhelev+ziezilabs@gmail.com</a>.
    App-specific contact addresses are listed within each app&rsquo;s policy.
  </p>

  <footer>
    <p>&copy; 2026 Ziezi Labs.</p>
  </footer>

</main>
</body>
</html>
